<plot>"Love Potion" presents a fascinating behind-the-scenes look at the staging and rehearsals with Stage Director Frank Dunlop and filming by Brian Large of this celebrated production of "L'elisir d'amore". Featuring interviews with the cast and the opera's dazzling married stars, Angela Gheorghiu and Roberto Alagna. A unique insight into the world of opera recording.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?344879</url></doc>
